Content:: Anwar Hussain Laskar (28 December 1964 – 18 July 2022), also known as Rana Bhai, was an Indian politician.[1] He was a member of the Assam Legislative Assembly from 1996 to 2006, elected from Sonai.[2] He was a member of Asom Gana Parishad and later the Samajwadi Party.[2]  This article about a politician from Assam is a stub.
